When three friends (Ed Helms, Zach Galifianakis 
and Bradley Cooper) finally come to after a raucous 
night of bachelor-party revelry, they find a baby 
in the closet and a tiger in the bathroom. But 
they can't seem to locate their best friend, Doug 
(Justin Bartha) -- who's supposed to be tying the 
knot. Launching a frantic search for Doug, the trio 
perseveres through a dandy hangover to try to make 
it to the church on time.
